(3147, 'Crestolip 10 mg 30 f.c.tabs.', 'كريستوليب 10 مجم 30 قرص', '90', '108', 'Rosuvastatin', 'Global napi pharmaceuticals', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'علاج إرتفاع الكولسترول في الدم', 'Antihyperlipidemic.statins', '10 mg', 'The FDA monograph states that rosuvastatin is indicated as an adjunct to diet in the treatment of triglyceridemia, Primary Dysbetalipoproteinemia (Type III Hyperlipoproteinemia), and Homozygous Familial Hypercholesterolemia.[F4649]
